{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7063b7a8ec","title":"朱瑞支队的作战部署叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"83d0e06e2f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"7063b7a8ec"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ce3763c927","type":"paragraph","text":"朱瑞支队的作战部署叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"4b9a3b2fca","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年11月18日）彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"12471c780c","type":"paragraph","text":"朱瑞可支队附电台，以经豫旺堡以西取间道急行军进同心城、豫旺堡城之间，相机袭击胡宗南指挥部（王家团庄），或抚乱周孔两师后尾为宜。推须注意马鸿宾部","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"669847a115","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"7a7d5e02c5","type":"paragraph","text":"十八日八时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"a02b0cf675","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东给红军前敌总指挥兼政治委员、第一方面军司令员彭德怀的电报。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"7040ec3007","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]朱瑞，当时任红军第一方面军第一军团政治部主任。他临时率第一方面军特务团与第一军团教导营在今宁夏同心县豫旺堡附近地区活动。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"a507a007a2","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]胡宗南，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第一路第二纵队司令兼第一师师长。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"b45b53dbdf","type":"paragraph","text":"14]周孔两师，指国民党军西北“”总司令部第一路第二纵队第四十三师和第九十七师，师长分别为周祥初和孔令愉。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"},{"id":"057804b4e3","type":"paragraph","text":"[5]马鸿宾，当时任国民党军西北“剩”总司令部第一路第四纵队司令兼第三十五师师长。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec"}],"page":{"id":"ed4f51bc44","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"7063b7a8ec","start":3,"end":3}}}},"__N_SSG":true}